  <summary date="2023-10-13T12:58:18Z" status="Introduced in House">Preserving Family Farms Act of 2023

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase to $13 million (currently, $750,000) the limitation on the special use valuation for farmland or other trades or businesses for estate tax purposes. The increased amount is adjusted for inflation for estates of decedents dying after 2023.</summary>
